	image synthesis packages.
	Adrian Clarke <alien@essex.ac.uk>

barkley.berkeley.edu [128.32.142.237] : tcl/extensions/tsipp3.0b.tar.Z -
	*Tcl-SIPP*
	Mark Diekhans <markd@grizzly.com or markd@NeoSoft.com>

